WEBVTT

00:00.251 --> 00:03.124
"IT WAS BAGHEERA
THE BLACK PANTHER,

00:03.124 --> 00:04.925
"INKY BLACK ALL OVER,

00:04.925 --> 00:07.298
"BUT WITH THE PANTHER MARKINGS
SHOWING UP IN CERTAIN LIGHTS

00:07.298 --> 00:09.760
"LIKE THE PATTERN
OF WATERED SILK.

00:09.760 --> 00:12.933
HE HAD A VOICE
AS SOFT AS WILD HONEY."

00:12.933 --> 00:15.056
MMM.

00:15.056 --> 00:16.517
DELICIOUS.

00:16.517 --> 00:18.099
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:18.099 --> 00:19.520
I MEAN THAT.

00:19.520 --> 00:21.982
WHEN I READ THE WORDS
"WILD HONEY,"

00:21.982 --> 00:24.275
IT LIT UP
MY GUSTATORY CORTEX --

00:24.275 --> 00:27.278
THE REGION OF THE BRAIN
THAT REGISTERS TASTE.

00:27.278 --> 00:30.571
AND "WATERED SILK" TRIGGERED
MY SOMATOSENSORY CORTEX,

00:30.571 --> 00:33.614
HOME TO MY SENSE OF TOUCH.

00:33.614 --> 00:35.996
THAT'S WHY
WHEN WE READ LITERATURE,

00:35.996 --> 00:37.618
IT MAKES US FEEL ALIVE --

00:37.618 --> 00:40.711
IT SERVES UP A-A FEAST
FOR THE SENSES.

00:40.711 --> 00:44.545
SO, THIS WEEKEND, I AM
CHALLENGING MR. LEWICKI HERE

00:44.545 --> 00:46.877
TO PUT DOWN THE COMIC BOOKS

00:46.877 --> 00:49.970
AND PICK UP SOME KIPLING
OR SOME FAULKNER OR SOME JOYCE.

00:49.970 --> 00:52.133
AND IT WOULDN'T KILL
YOU KNUCKLEHEADS

00:52.133 --> 00:53.474
TO DO THE SAME THING.

00:55.266 --> 00:56.807
Donnie:
WHATCHA WRITING?

00:56.807 --> 00:58.729
NO PEEKING.

00:58.729 --> 01:01.312
[ Chuckling ] WHAT,
ARE YOU KEEPING A DIARY NOW --

01:01.312 --> 01:03.144
LITTLE I's
DOTTED WITH HEARTS?

01:03.144 --> 01:04.395
VERY FUNNY.

01:04.395 --> 01:07.238
UH, IT'S MY VOWS
FOR THE WEDDING.

01:07.238 --> 01:09.150
THOUGHT FATHER PAT
WANTED THOSE YESTERDAY.

01:09.150 --> 01:12.823
I KNOW. I AM JUST, UH,
JUST TWEAKING THEM A LITTLE.

01:12.823 --> 01:14.405
YOU'RE NOT EVEN CLOSE
TO FINISHED, ARE YOU?

01:14.405 --> 01:17.368
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

01:17.368 --> 01:18.499
MORETTI.

01:21.752 --> 01:23.414
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

01:23.414 --> 01:25.416
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER,
SIRENS WAILING ]

01:25.416 --> 01:27.418
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

01:34.555 --> 01:36.096
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI,
FBI.

01:36.096 --> 01:39.600
WE'RE GOOD HERE.
OPEN-AND-SHUT CASE.

01:39.600 --> 01:41.602
YOU MIND GIVING ME THE DETAILS
ANYWAY? YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

01:41.602 --> 01:43.604
I DON'T WANT TO GO BACK
TO THE BOSS EMPTY-HANDED.

01:44.725 --> 01:46.857
GUY UNDER THE SHEET
IS AHMAD KHAN,

01:46.857 --> 01:48.649
CONSUL GENERAL
OF BANGLADESH.

01:48.649 --> 01:52.072
HE WAS STABBED IN THE NECK
BY HIS SECRETARY.

01:52.072 --> 01:53.824
WOMAN'S NAME
IS NASIM SHAH.

01:53.824 --> 01:55.576
SHE CONFESS?

01:55.576 --> 01:58.499
DIDN'T HAVE TO. SHE WAS FOUND
HOLDING THE MURDER WEAPON.

01:58.499 --> 02:00.161
SHE'S ON HER WAY
TO COUNTY LOCKUP.

02:00.161 --> 02:02.413
YOU WANT TO MUSCLE IN
ON A CASE,

02:02.413 --> 02:03.794
I GOT
A DOZEN OPEN HOMICIDES.

02:03.794 --> 02:05.416
YOU'RE NOT TAKING
THIS ONE.

02:05.416 --> 02:07.418
"TAKING"?
IT'S FBI JURISDICTION.

02:07.418 --> 02:09.420
THE VICTIM'S
A FOREIGN OFFICIAL.

02:09.420 --> 02:11.712
AND HE WAS MURDERED
ON A CITY STREET.

02:11.712 --> 02:14.134
THIS CASE
BELONGS TO THE CPD.

02:24.725 --> 02:27.358
[ BUZZER ]

02:27.358 --> 02:30.401
MS. SHAH?
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI, FBI.

02:30.401 --> 02:32.653
I'D LIKE TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED TONIGHT.

02:32.653 --> 02:34.655
I SWEAR, I DID NOT
KILL THE CONSUL.

02:34.655 --> 02:36.577
THE POLICE
WILL NOT LISTEN TO ME.

02:36.577 --> 02:37.868
OKAY.

02:37.868 --> 02:40.160
JUST...
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

02:41.872 --> 02:44.415
UH, M-MR. KHAN
HAD JUST LEFT THE OFFICE.

02:44.415 --> 02:46.917
HE WAS MEETING SOME FRIENDS
FOR DINNER

02:46.917 --> 02:49.129
A FEW BLOCKS
FROM THE CONSULATE.

02:49.129 --> 02:52.673
BUT THEN I REALIZED THAT HE HAD
LEFT HIS PHONE IN THE OFFICE.

02:52.673 --> 02:54.215
AND SO
I WENT AFTER HIM.

02:54.215 --> 02:56.257
MR. KHAN?

03:09.480 --> 03:11.111
[ GASPS ]

03:12.112 --> 03:14.275
THE PAIN WAS EXCRUCIATING.

03:16.026 --> 03:18.619
I MANAGED TO CRAWL OVER
TO MR. KHAN

03:18.619 --> 03:21.282
TO PULL OUT THE KNIFE.

03:21.282 --> 03:22.413
[ GASPS ]

03:22.413 --> 03:24.875
THAT'S WHEN I FAINTED.

03:26.877 --> 03:30.381
DID I MISS SOMETHING?
WERE YOU ATTACKED, AS WELL?

03:31.672 --> 03:34.094
N-NO.

03:34.094 --> 03:35.636
NO.

03:35.636 --> 03:37.928
BUT WHEN I SEE
SOMEONE IN PAIN,

03:37.928 --> 03:40.551
THEIR SUFFERING
BECOMES MY SUFFERING.

03:40.551 --> 03:45.846
SO YOU'RE SAYING YOU LITERALLY
FELT LIKE YOU HAD BEEN STABBED

03:45.846 --> 03:47.478
AND THE PAIN
MADE YOU PASS OUT?

03:47.478 --> 03:49.400
I KNOW HOW IT SOUNDS.

03:49.400 --> 03:52.563
BUT EVERYTHING I'VE TOLD YOU
IS TRUE.

03:52.563 --> 03:54.655
[ SIGHS SHAKILY ]

03:56.487 --> 03:58.909
[ SNIFFLES ]
CHANDRA IS PUNISHING ME.

03:58.909 --> 04:00.321
CHANDRA?

04:00.321 --> 04:02.323
[ SNIFFLES ]
THE HINDU GOD OF THE MOON.

04:02.323 --> 04:04.244
IN OUR CULTURE,

04:04.244 --> 04:08.078
WE BEAR THE BURDENS OF SINS
COMMITTED IN OUR PAST LIVES.

04:10.421 --> 04:12.423
THIS IS MY CURSE.

04:18.589 --> 04:20.761
Man: CLEAR THE GATE.

04:20.761 --> 04:23.183
GATE CLEAR.

04:23.183 --> 04:25.766
Daniel: HERE SHE IS.

04:25.766 --> 04:28.188
[ DOOR CREAKS, CLOSES ]

04:28.188 --> 04:30.941
MS. SHAH, THIS IS MY ASSOCIATE
DR. PIERCE.

04:30.941 --> 04:33.944
HE HAS A FEW QUESTIONS
HE'D LIKE TO ASK YOU.

04:38.859 --> 04:40.781
ARE YOU OKAY?

04:40.781 --> 04:43.283
THE WOMAN IN MY CELL
IS SICK.

04:43.283 --> 04:45.035
ALL NIGHT, SHE WAS CRYING,

04:45.035 --> 04:47.668
SAYING THAT SHE WOULD DIE
WITHOUT A FIX.

04:47.668 --> 04:50.621
NOW SHE IS QUIET,
BUT SHE CANNOT STOP SHAKING.

04:50.621 --> 04:52.172
OW!
OW!

04:52.172 --> 04:53.544
SORRY.
JUST CONFIRMING MY THEORY.

04:53.544 --> 04:55.215
I'M FINE.
THANKS FOR ASKING.

04:55.215 --> 04:57.628
WHEN DID YOU START EXPERIENCING
OTHER PEOPLE'S PAIN?

04:59.720 --> 05:02.132
WHEN I WAS 5,

05:02.132 --> 05:06.056
A BOY IN MY VILLAGE TRIPPED
MY SISTER AND BROKE HER LEG.

05:06.056 --> 05:09.560
I FELL DOWN, TOO,
BECAUSE THE PAIN WAS SO INTENSE.

05:09.560 --> 05:13.313
THAT'S WHEN THE VILLAGE ELDERS
SAID THAT I WAS CURSED.

05:13.313 --> 05:14.645
YOU'RE NOT CURSED.

05:14.645 --> 05:16.737
I THINK YOU HAVE
A NEUROLOGICAL CONDITION

05:16.737 --> 05:19.490
CALLED
MIRROR-TOUCH SYNESTHESIA.

05:19.490 --> 05:22.242
I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

05:22.242 --> 05:24.324
WHEN MOST OF US
SEE SOMEONE BEING TOUCHED,

05:24.324 --> 05:25.906
OUR BRAINS
CREATE A SIMULATION

05:25.906 --> 05:27.948
OF WHAT WE THINK
THAT TOUCH FEELS LIKE.

05:27.948 --> 05:29.249
BUT WHEN YOU SEE SOMEONE

05:29.249 --> 05:32.162
BEING CARESSED OR --
OR PINCHED OR STABBED,

05:32.162 --> 05:34.835
YOUR BRAIN RESPONDS
AS IF IT WAS HAPPENING TO YOU.

05:34.835 --> 05:36.957
I'M GUESSING YOU ALSO KNOW
WHAT PEOPLE ARE FEELING --

05:36.957 --> 05:39.049
WHETHER THEY'RE HAPPY,
SAD, JEALOUS?
YES.

05:39.049 --> 05:41.672
THAT'S BECAUSE YOUR BRAIN
MIMICS EMOTIONAL REACTIONS, TOO.

05:41.672 --> 05:43.464
WE ALL MAKE
MICRO-FACIAL EXPRESSIONS

05:43.464 --> 05:45.175
THAT TELEGRAPH
WHAT WE'RE FEELING.

05:45.175 --> 05:46.677
MOST PEOPLE
CAN'T PERCEIVE THEM,

05:46.677 --> 05:49.770
BUT A SYNESTHETE
UNCONSCIOUSLY PICKS UP ON THEM.

05:49.770 --> 05:51.432
SHE'S AT THE MERCY
OF EVERYONE AROUND HER

05:51.432 --> 05:53.474
AND WHATEVER
THEY'RE GOING THROUGH.

05:53.474 --> 05:55.856
SHE WOULDN'T STAB ANYONE.
IT'D BE LIKE PLUNGING
A KNIFE INTO HER OWN NECK.

05:55.856 --> 05:57.398
YES. THAT'S EXACTLY IT.

05:57.398 --> 06:00.691
P-PLEASE, PLEASE, CAN YOU GET ME
OUT OF THIS PLACE?

06:03.444 --> 06:05.406
SO, YOU THINK
THIS WOMAN IS INNOCENT,

06:05.406 --> 06:07.868
BUT YOU WANT ME TO CHARGE HER
WITH MURDER ANYWAY.

06:07.868 --> 06:08.989
WHY?

06:08.989 --> 06:10.831
LOOK, SHE'S UNUSUAL,
ALL RIGHT?

06:10.831 --> 06:12.703
SHE LITERALLY
HAD WITHDRAWAL SYMPTOMS

06:12.703 --> 06:14.665
JUST BECAUSE THE JUNKIE
IN THE CELL WITH HER DID, TOO.

06:14.665 --> 06:17.257
DANIEL SAYS THAT SHE
COULD SUFFER A SERIOUS
PSYCHOLOGICAL BREAKDOWN

06:17.257 --> 06:18.839
IF WE DON'T GET HER
OUT OF COUNTY LOCKUP.

06:18.839 --> 06:20.050
AND TAKE HER WHERE?

06:20.050 --> 06:21.422
IT'S NOT LIKE
THINGS ARE GONNA BE

06:21.422 --> 06:22.763
MUCH BETTER FOR HER
AT A FEDERAL JAIL.

06:22.763 --> 06:24.304
WELL, ONCE YOU CHARGE HER,

06:24.304 --> 06:26.597
WE CAN PUT HER IN A MOTEL
WITH A MARSHAL WATCHING HER.

06:26.597 --> 06:29.430
MEANWHILE, DANIEL AND I
WILL GO FIND THE REAL KILLER,

06:29.430 --> 06:31.391
AND THEN
YOU CAN DROP THE CHARGES.

06:31.391 --> 06:33.013
AH. I SEE.

06:33.013 --> 06:35.315
AND I'M SUPPOSED TO SELL
THIS LITTLE PLAN OF YOURS

06:35.315 --> 06:37.067
TO A JUDGE
HOW, EXACTLY?

06:37.067 --> 06:40.070
IF NASIM...
STAYS IN JAIL...

06:40.070 --> 06:41.902
SHE COULD SEE SOMEONE
GET SHANKED,

06:41.902 --> 06:44.324
PASS OUT AGAIN
FROM THE PAIN.

06:44.324 --> 06:47.077
YOU'D BE LOOKING
AT A BRAIN INJURY, MAYBE WORSE.

06:47.077 --> 06:49.029
"FOREIGN NATIONAL DIES
IN U.S. CUSTODY" --

06:49.029 --> 06:51.031
THAT'S NOT A HEADLINE
ANYONE WANTS TO SEE, RIGHT?

06:51.031 --> 06:52.583
MNH-MNH.

06:52.583 --> 06:54.334
I HOPE YOU'RE PUTTING
SOME OF THAT CREATIVITY

06:54.334 --> 06:55.335
INTO YOUR VOWS.

06:59.169 --> 07:00.841
AGENT MORETTI,
DR. PIERCE.

07:03.173 --> 07:05.005
I'M VICE-CONSUL
RASHID PRASAD.

07:05.966 --> 07:07.097
PLEASE.

07:07.097 --> 07:10.350
THANK YOU
FOR MAKING TIME FOR US.

07:10.350 --> 07:12.012
YOU HAVE
OUR CONDOLENCES.

07:12.012 --> 07:13.313
THANK YOU.

07:13.313 --> 07:15.105
THE CONSUL WAS A MAN
OF GREAT SERVICE.

07:15.105 --> 07:17.898
AND NASIM IS ADORED
BY EVERYONE HERE.

07:17.898 --> 07:20.771
I CAN'T BELIEVE
SHE WOULD HARM ANYONE.

07:20.771 --> 07:22.272
WE AGREE.

07:22.272 --> 07:23.564
GOOD.

07:23.564 --> 07:25.696
THERE MUST BE
SOME OTHER EXPLANATION.

07:25.696 --> 07:28.949
YOU KNOW, THERE'S A FACILITY
FOR THE MENTALLY ILL NEARBY.

07:28.949 --> 07:31.742
PERHAPS ONE OF THOSE PEOPLE
GOT LOOSE.

07:31.742 --> 07:33.203
"THOSE PEOPLE"?

07:33.203 --> 07:35.245
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
NOW THAT THE CONSUL IS GONE,

07:35.245 --> 07:37.127
YOU'RE IN CHARGE HERE NOW,
IS THAT RIGHT?

07:37.127 --> 07:38.749
TEMPORARILY.

07:38.749 --> 07:41.672
I'M STILL VICE-CONSUL
UNTIL A NEW APPOINTMENT IS MADE.

07:41.672 --> 07:43.884
I'M SURE IT'S A VERY SHORT LIST
OF CANDIDATES --

07:43.884 --> 07:45.966
WITH YOUR NAME
AT THE TOP?

07:45.966 --> 07:48.639
I DON'T APPRECIATE
WHAT YOU'RE IMPLYING.

07:48.639 --> 07:51.802
WE DO NEED TO BE THOROUGH IN
OUR INVESTIGATION, MR. PRASAD.

07:51.802 --> 07:53.473
I'M SURE THAT YOU CAN
APPRECIATE THAT.

07:53.473 --> 07:54.474
OF COURSE.

07:54.474 --> 07:56.146
BUT I ASSURE YOU,

07:56.146 --> 07:59.860
THIS IS NOT HOW I WOULD CHOOSE
TO ADVANCE MY CAREER.

07:59.860 --> 08:03.654
DID THE CONSUL HAVE ANY ENEMIES
THAT YOU'RE AWARE OF?

08:03.654 --> 08:05.566
NO.

08:05.566 --> 08:08.569
BUT YOU SHOULD TALK TO THE HEAD
OF OUR SECURITY, OFFICER MEHTA.

08:10.701 --> 08:13.493
THERE WERE NO SPECIFIC THREATS
AGAINST THE CONSUL

08:13.493 --> 08:14.745
THAT I KNEW OF.

08:14.745 --> 08:16.917
BUT THERE WAS
A-AN INCIDENT

08:16.917 --> 08:18.669
A FEW HOURS BEFORE
THE CONSUL WAS MURDERED.

08:18.669 --> 08:19.750
TELL US ABOUT IT.

08:19.750 --> 08:21.832
[ SIGHS ]

08:21.832 --> 08:23.674
A REPORTER SHOWED UP,

08:23.674 --> 08:26.627
CLAIMING TO BE WRITING AN EXPOSÃ©
FOR THE CHICAGO STAR-HERALD.

08:26.627 --> 08:28.969
THE CONSUL TOLD ME
HE'D ALREADY GIVEN THIS REPORTER

08:28.969 --> 08:32.182
AN INTERVIEW A FEW WEEKS BEFORE,
TOLD ME TO TURN HIM AWAY.

08:32.182 --> 08:34.514
WHEN I DID,
THE REPORTER GOT VERY ANGRY.

08:34.514 --> 08:36.516
STARTED MAKING ACCUS--

08:40.601 --> 08:43.694
...ACCUSATIONS
REGARDING THE CONSUL.

08:43.694 --> 08:45.195
SUCH AS?

08:46.356 --> 08:47.698
[ SIGHS ]

08:47.698 --> 08:49.319
PLEASE UNDERSTAND,

08:49.319 --> 08:51.952
I DON'T WISH TO INSULT
THE INTEGRITY OF THE CONSUL,

08:51.952 --> 08:54.534
PARTICULARLY NOW
THAT HE CAN'T DEFEND HIMSELF.

08:54.534 --> 08:57.618
OFFICER MEHTA,
ANYTHING YOU SHARE WITH US

08:57.618 --> 08:59.539
MAY HELP US
FIND HIS KILLER.

09:01.752 --> 09:02.753
OF COURSE.

09:02.753 --> 09:04.334
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

09:06.166 --> 09:08.589
THE REPORTER SAID
THAT THE CONSUL WAS RESPONSIBLE

09:08.589 --> 09:11.131
FOR THE DEATHS OF THOUSANDS
OF PEOPLE IN BANGLADESH.

09:11.131 --> 09:13.804
WHAT DID HE MEAN
BY THAT?

09:13.804 --> 09:15.555
HE DIDN'T SAY
SPECIFICALLY --

09:15.555 --> 09:17.557
JUST THAT IT WAS RELATED
TO THE RECENT CHOLERA EPIDEMIC.

09:17.557 --> 09:19.730
HE ALSO GAVE ME THIS.

09:23.644 --> 09:26.987
HE SAID TO CALL HIM
IF I CARED ABOUT JUSTICE.

09:30.030 --> 09:31.071
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

09:31.071 --> 09:32.993
MR. PINEDA?

09:39.499 --> 09:41.001
[ ENGINE IDLING ]

09:41.001 --> 09:43.583
YOU HEAR THAT?

09:43.583 --> 09:45.585
IT'S A CAR RUNNING.

09:50.841 --> 09:53.093
MR. PINEDA?

09:53.093 --> 09:54.845
[ SCOFFS ]

10:02.522 --> 10:04.104
[ DOORKNOB RATTLING ]

10:04.104 --> 10:05.435
I GOT IT. I GOT IT.

10:08.528 --> 10:10.280
HOLD YOUR BREATH.

10:14.494 --> 10:15.615
[ COUGHS ]

10:15.615 --> 10:17.658
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

10:19.539 --> 10:20.701
GRAB HIS FEET.

10:26.546 --> 10:28.628
[ COUGHING ]

10:46.106 --> 10:49.940
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER,
SIRENS WAILING ]

10:49.940 --> 10:51.231
WHAT'S THIS?

10:51.231 --> 10:52.442
DIAZEPAM.

10:52.442 --> 10:53.904
ONE OF THE CRIME TECHS
FOUND IT

10:53.904 --> 10:55.485
ON AN END TABLE
IN THE LIVING ROOM.

10:55.485 --> 10:56.867
NOT UNCOMMON WITH SUICIDE.

10:56.867 --> 10:58.448
TAKES THE EDGE OFF
SO THEY CAN DO THE DEED.

10:58.448 --> 10:59.910
'COURSE,
THIS WASN'T A SUICIDE.

10:59.910 --> 11:01.541
DANIEL, NO.
COME ON, KATE.

11:01.541 --> 11:03.583
A REPORTER ACCUSES
THE BANGLADESHI CONSUL

11:03.583 --> 11:04.955
OF BEING COMPLICIT
SOMEHOW

11:04.955 --> 11:06.997
IN THE DEATHS
OF THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE,

11:06.997 --> 11:09.589
AND WITHIN A DAY, THE REPORTER
AND THE CONSUL WIND UP DEAD?

11:09.589 --> 11:11.001
IF SOMEONE WANTED
TO MURDER PINEDA,

11:11.001 --> 11:12.462
THERE ARE MUCH EASIER WAYS
OF DOING IT

11:12.462 --> 11:13.794
THAN DRAGGING HIM
INTO A CAR

11:13.794 --> 11:15.595
AND FORCING HIM
TO INHALE EXHAUST FUMES.

11:15.595 --> 11:17.347
SO MAYBE HE WAS ALREADY DEAD
WHEN THEY PUT HIM IN THE CAR.

11:17.347 --> 11:19.389
THE M.E. SAID
THAT HIS SKIN DISCOLORATION

11:19.389 --> 11:21.601
IS CONSISTENT WITH
CARBON MONOXIDE POISONING.

11:21.601 --> 11:23.433
OKAY, SO MAYBE HE WAS
UNCONSCIOUS. I DON'T KNOW.

11:23.433 --> 11:25.225
WE NEED TO FIND OUT
WHATEVER STORY THAT
REPORTER WAS WORKING ON.

11:25.225 --> 11:26.767
I MEAN,
THAT'S GOT TO BE PART OF IT.

11:26.767 --> 11:28.769
I'LL HAVE CYBER GO THROUGH
HIS PHONE AND COMPUTER.

11:28.769 --> 11:30.520
WHAT ABOUT THE CRIME
SCENE PHOTOS? YOU CAN
GET YOUR HANDS ON THOSE?

11:30.520 --> 11:32.112
I'LL GET THEM FOR YOU,
BUT RIGHT NOW,

11:32.112 --> 11:33.864
THERE'S JUST SOMEWHERE ELSE
THAT I'VE GOT TO BE.

11:43.033 --> 11:46.126
Father Pat:
WELL, NOBODY SERVES BETTER
GREASY FOOD THAN MORETTI'S.

11:46.126 --> 11:48.538
PLENTY MORE
WHERE THAT CAME FROM.

11:48.538 --> 11:50.881
NOW, WHY ARE YOU TRYING
TO PLY ME WITH FOOD?

11:50.881 --> 11:52.542
COME ON, FATHER PAT.

11:52.542 --> 11:54.965
CAN'T A COUPLE OF OLD FRIENDS
JUST GET TOGETHER FOR A BITE?

11:57.547 --> 11:59.179
OKAY, HERE'S THE THING.

11:59.179 --> 12:01.551
I'M HOPING THAT YOU CAN LET ME
GET A LOOK AT DONNIE'S VOWS.

12:01.551 --> 12:03.303
DON'T YOU WANT TO WAIT
TILL THE WEDDING DAY?

12:04.724 --> 12:06.646
LOOK,
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE

12:06.646 --> 12:09.309
THAT DONNIE AND I
ARE ON THE SAME WAVELENGTH.

12:09.309 --> 12:11.111
I DON'T WANT
TO WRITE SOMETHING FUNNY

12:11.111 --> 12:13.653
IF HE'S WRITTEN SOMETHING
MORE SERIOUS OR VICE VERSA.

12:13.653 --> 12:15.565
SO YOU HAVEN'T
WRITTEN YOURS YET.

12:15.565 --> 12:18.738
WHY DOES EVERYONE ASSUME THAT?
YES. I'VE WRITTEN LOTS OF VOWS.

12:18.738 --> 12:21.241
JUST NONE THAT I LIKE.

12:21.241 --> 12:22.662
FINE.

12:22.662 --> 12:24.074
BUT YOU'RE NOT GONNA GET
THE INSPIRATION YOU NEED

12:24.074 --> 12:25.125
FROM DONNIE'S.

12:25.125 --> 12:26.326
WHY DO YOU THINK THAT?

12:26.326 --> 12:27.828
'CAUSE I'M NOT
GONNA SHOW THEM TO YOU.

12:27.828 --> 12:30.170
IT'S NOT FAIR TO DONNIE,
FIRST OF ALL.

12:30.170 --> 12:32.752
AND SECOND OF ALL, I HAPPEN
TO REMEMBER "MOUNT MORETTI."

12:32.752 --> 12:34.254
WHAT?

12:34.254 --> 12:35.926
THAT AMAZING VOLCANO
THAT YOU BUILT

12:35.926 --> 12:37.838
FOR SISTER MARGARET'S
SCIENCE FAIR IN THE 4th GRADE.

12:37.838 --> 12:39.880
YOU SPENT DAYS COMPLAINING
THAT YOU COULDN'T DO IT.

12:39.880 --> 12:41.591
THEN THE NIGHT BEFORE,
YOU PULLED IT OFF,

12:41.591 --> 12:42.682
WON THE WHOLE SCIENCE FAIR.

12:42.682 --> 12:44.644
YOU CAN DO THIS, KATE.

12:44.644 --> 12:46.516
BUT WHY DO I HAVE TO?

12:46.516 --> 12:48.849
IT'S A TRADITIONAL
CATHOLIC CEREMONY.

12:48.849 --> 12:50.600
WE'RE NOT EVEN
SUPPOSED TO WRITE OUR OWN VOWS.

12:50.600 --> 12:53.313
THERE'S NOTHING TRADITIONAL
ABOUT YOU TWO GETTING MARRIED,

12:53.313 --> 12:55.695
DIVORCED, ANNULLED,
THEN REMARRIED.

12:57.858 --> 12:59.449
THIS IS
WHAT DONNIE WANTED TO DO,

12:59.449 --> 13:00.951
SO THIS IS
WHAT WE'RE GONNA DO.

13:00.951 --> 13:02.782
[ SIGHS ]

13:12.542 --> 13:14.374
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
[ Australian accent ]
HEY, HEY, HEY.

13:14.374 --> 13:16.086
TAKE IT EASY, MATE.
I'M A FRIEND.

13:16.086 --> 13:17.677
I'VE NEVER SEEN YOU BEFORE
IN MY LIFE.

13:17.677 --> 13:19.339
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU GOT IN HERE, BUT --

13:19.339 --> 13:20.921
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
UH, SORRY.

13:20.921 --> 13:23.553
I'M A FRIEND OF NATALIE'S.

13:25.265 --> 13:26.806
GREAT.

13:26.806 --> 13:29.930
MY HALLUCINATIONS ARE
MAKING FRIENDS WITH EACH OTHER.

13:29.930 --> 13:30.891
[ LAUGHS ]

13:30.891 --> 13:32.392
YEAH, WE ARE.

13:32.392 --> 13:34.895
MET NATALIE A FEW MONTHS AGO
IN BANGLADESH.

13:34.895 --> 13:37.938
PBHT. WHAT A GREAT LADY.
JUST AN AMAZING ENERGY.

13:37.938 --> 13:39.900
WHEN I TOLD HER
I WAS HEADED TO CHICAGO,

13:39.900 --> 13:41.571
SHE SAID
I SHOULD CRASH WITH YOU.

13:41.571 --> 13:44.074
NATALIE WOULD NEVER
SAY SOMETHING SAY THAT.

13:44.074 --> 13:46.496
WELL, SHE WAS ON
A SPIRITUAL SABBATICAL.

13:46.496 --> 13:48.208
THAT DOESN'T SOUND LIKE HER
AT ALL.

13:48.208 --> 13:49.950
NO, SHE'S MADE SOME INCREDIBLE
PROGRESS IN HER PRACTICE

13:49.950 --> 13:51.371
SINCE SHE LEFT HERE.

13:51.371 --> 13:53.503
SHE'S REALLY DISCOVERED
HER BLISS, YOU KNOW?

13:53.503 --> 13:55.215
SHE'S SO MUCH HAPPIER.

13:55.215 --> 13:59.169
AND THE, UH...THE FEW DAYS
THAT WE SPENT TOGETHER

13:59.169 --> 14:03.223
WERE, UH...
MUTUALLY SPIRITUAL...

14:03.223 --> 14:04.464
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:04.464 --> 14:06.346
...IF YOU CATCH MY DRIFT.

14:06.346 --> 14:07.767
OKAY. GET OUT.

14:07.767 --> 14:09.639
MATE, I'M SENSING
SOME REAL HOSTILITY HERE.

14:09.639 --> 14:11.311
REALLY? REALLY?

14:11.311 --> 14:13.313
YOU'RE VULGAR AND DISGUSTING,
AND I-I CAN'T BEAR THE THOUGHT

14:13.313 --> 14:15.395
OF YOU AND NATALIE
HAVING MUTUAL...ANYTHING,

14:15.395 --> 14:17.107
EVEN IF YOU ARE
BOTH IMAGINARY.

14:17.107 --> 14:20.030
NOW GO. GET YOUR FILTHY FEET OFF
MY COUCH AND OUT OF MY HOUSE.

14:20.030 --> 14:21.611
THEY'RE NOT EVEN
THAT DIRTY.

14:21.611 --> 14:23.613
OH, ARE YOU KI--
LOOK AT THEM. THEY'RE FI--

14:35.375 --> 14:38.378
Dr. Swank: I'LL BE DAMNED IF
YOU WEREN'T RIGHT, DR. PIERCE.

14:38.378 --> 14:41.381
THERE IS
A MICROSCOPIC PUNCTURE MARK

14:41.381 --> 14:42.672
ALONG THE HAIRLINE

14:42.672 --> 14:46.466
WITH RESIDUAL TRACES
OF DIAZEPAM AROUND IT.

14:46.466 --> 14:49.139
EXPLAINS THE METABOLIZED LEVELS
WE FOUND IN HIS BLOODSTREAM.

14:49.139 --> 14:50.850
ENOUGH
TO KNOCK OUT A HORSE.

14:50.850 --> 14:52.472
WOULD'VE ASSUMED IT WAS FROM
THE PILLS IF YOU HADN'T CALLED.

14:52.472 --> 14:53.934
WELL,
IT'S PRACTICALLY INVISIBLE.

14:55.725 --> 14:57.147
HOW THE HELL
DID YOU KNOW TO LOOK?

14:57.147 --> 14:58.898
HIS FEET WERE CLEAN.

14:58.898 --> 15:00.020
I'M SORRY.
COME AGAIN?

15:00.020 --> 15:01.821
IT RAINED THAT NIGHT.

15:01.821 --> 15:04.324
THE YARD BETWEEN PINEDA'S HOUSE
AND THE GARAGE WAS A MESS.

15:04.324 --> 15:06.076
IF HE'D GONE OUT THERE
TO KILL HIMSELF,

15:06.076 --> 15:07.737
HIS FEET WOULD'VE BEEN
COVERED WITH MUD.

15:07.737 --> 15:10.830
I THINK THE KILLER
BROKE INTO THE HOUSE...

15:10.830 --> 15:13.913
FOUND PINEDA SLEEPING,
INJECTED HIM WITH DIAZEPAM...

15:15.165 --> 15:16.746
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

15:16.746 --> 15:19.089
...SUBDUED HIM -- WHICH WOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN THAT HARD

15:19.089 --> 15:20.670
BECAUSE OF THE VALIUM...

15:23.843 --> 15:25.545
...THEN LEFT THOSE PILLS
ON THE END TABLE

15:25.545 --> 15:28.178
TO ACCOUNT FOR THE DRUG
SHOWING UP IN THE TOX REPORT.

15:28.178 --> 15:31.181
HE TOOK PINEDA'S BODY
THROUGH THE YARD,

15:31.181 --> 15:35.685
MAKING SURE THAT HE DIDN'T
GET FOOTPRINTS IN THE GARAGE,

15:35.685 --> 15:38.108
PUT HIM IN THE CAR...

15:38.108 --> 15:39.519
STARTED THE ENGINE...

15:39.519 --> 15:42.692
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

15:43.613 --> 15:45.025
...AND LEFT HIM TO DIE.

15:45.025 --> 15:47.527
PRETTY SLICK.
SOUNDS PROFESSIONAL.

15:47.527 --> 15:50.830
WELL, I'M CHANGING
THE CAUSE OF DEATH TO HOMICIDE.

15:57.998 --> 16:00.040
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING ]

16:05.885 --> 16:07.347
[ CLICK, MUSIC STOPS ]

16:07.347 --> 16:09.759
CYBER DIDN'T FIND ANYTHING
ON BANGLADESH OR CHOLERA

16:09.759 --> 16:11.181
ON SCOTT PINEDA'S COMPUTER.

16:11.181 --> 16:13.513
HIS HARD DRIVE WAS WIPED.
SO WAS HIS PHONE.

16:13.513 --> 16:15.055
AND THE EDITOR
AT THE STAR-HERALD

16:15.055 --> 16:16.766
SAID THAT PINEDA
NEVER FILED HIS STORY.

16:16.766 --> 16:18.398
WHAT ABOUT
PHONE-COMPANY RECORDS?

16:18.398 --> 16:21.441
THE LAST CALL PINEDA MADE
BEFORE HE DIED WAS TO A DOCTOR.

16:21.441 --> 16:23.653
HIS NAME IS...
TREVOR RHODES?

16:25.945 --> 16:28.568
SCOTT AND I
WERE ROOMMATES IN COLLEGE.

16:28.568 --> 16:30.200
WHY ARE YOU ASKING?

16:30.200 --> 16:32.032
HE WAS MURDERED
LAST NIGHT.

16:32.032 --> 16:35.035
I'M VERY SORRY.

16:35.035 --> 16:36.616
OH, GOD.

16:38.378 --> 16:39.879
I NEVER SHOULD'VE
TOLD HIM.

16:39.879 --> 16:41.711
TOLD HIM WHAT?

16:43.173 --> 16:45.625
I, UH...
I WORK IN INFECTIOUS DISEASES.

16:45.625 --> 16:48.218
I-I-I VOLUNTEER FOR
THE WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION.

16:48.218 --> 16:51.391
YOU WERE WORKING
IN BANGLADESH.

16:51.391 --> 16:53.012
YEAH.

16:53.012 --> 16:54.434
LAST YEAR, THEY HAD

16:54.434 --> 16:56.476
OVER A QUARTER MILLION CASES
OF CHOLERA.

16:56.476 --> 16:59.059
THE BANGLADESHIS TASK
THEIR INTERNATIONAL CONSULATES

16:59.059 --> 17:00.900
WITH SOURCING VACCINES.

17:00.900 --> 17:02.562
SIX MONTHS AGO,

17:02.562 --> 17:04.734
I HEARD THE CHICAGO CONSULATE
HAD ORDERED A SHIPMENT

17:04.734 --> 17:07.607
OF ONE OF THE NEWER ONES --
UH, BACTRA-VOX --

17:07.607 --> 17:09.989
FOR ONE OF THE POORER REGIONS
OF THE COUNTRY,

17:09.989 --> 17:12.322
SO I WENT TO BANGLADESH
TO HELP ADMINISTER IT,

17:12.322 --> 17:15.075
BUT WHEN THE SHIPMENT
ARRIVED...

17:15.075 --> 17:17.997
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

17:32.011 --> 17:33.673
DAMN IT.

17:33.673 --> 17:36.266
...I WAS PISSED,
BECAUSE INSTEAD OF BACTRA-VOX,

17:36.266 --> 17:40.100
THEY SENT US NUMORAL --
AN OUTDATED VACCINE.

17:40.100 --> 17:42.982
ALL I COULD DO WAS INOCULATE
THE LOCALS WITH WHAT WE HAD

17:42.982 --> 17:47.277
AND...PRAY TO GOD NO NEW STRAINS
OF CHOLERA APPEARED.

17:47.277 --> 17:49.949
LET ME GUESS --
YOUR PRAYERS WEREN'T ANSWERED.

17:49.949 --> 17:52.952
IT WAS DEVASTATING.

17:52.952 --> 17:56.956
THOUSANDS DIED --
MOSTLY KIDS, OLD PEOPLE.

17:59.999 --> 18:01.461
WHERE DOES SCOTT COME IN?

18:01.461 --> 18:03.463
[ SIGHS ]
WHEN I GOT BACK TO CHICAGO,

18:03.463 --> 18:05.465
UH, WE MET FOR DINNER
TO CATCH UP.

18:05.465 --> 18:07.587
I TOLD HIM ABOUT ALL THE MONEY
AND THE LIVES WASTED

18:07.587 --> 18:09.379
ON THIS OUTDATED VACCINE.

18:09.379 --> 18:11.090
AND PINEDA
SMELLED A STORY.

18:11.090 --> 18:14.013
WE BOTH JUST FIGURED IT WAS
BUREAUCRATIC INCOMPETENCE.

18:14.013 --> 18:16.636
BUT THEN SCOTT WENT
AND INTERVIEWED THE CONSUL,

18:16.636 --> 18:18.768
AND THE GUY LIED
RIGHT TO HIS FACE.

18:18.768 --> 18:21.481
HE KEPT INSISTING THAT
HE HAD BOUGHT THE NEWER VACCINE

18:21.481 --> 18:23.813
FOR HIS PEOPLE, NOT NUMORAL.

18:23.813 --> 18:25.315
MAYBE
THE CONSUL DIDN'T LIE.

18:25.315 --> 18:28.067
MAYBE NAVILET PHARMACEUTICALS
DID A BAIT-AND-SWITCH.

18:28.067 --> 18:29.899
WELL, THAT'S
WHAT WE THOUGHT, TOO.

18:29.899 --> 18:31.991
BUT THEN
SCOTT DID SOME DIGGING

18:31.991 --> 18:34.324
AND FOUND OUT
SOMETHING MUCH WORSE.

18:34.324 --> 18:36.156
THERE WAS A RUMOR

18:36.156 --> 18:38.738
THAT THE W.H.O.
WAS GOING TO DE-CERTIFY NUMORAL.

18:38.738 --> 18:41.451
SCOTT DISCOVERED THAT NAVILET
HAD A WHOLE STOCKPILE

18:41.451 --> 18:44.794
JUST SITTING IN A WAREHOUSE THAT
SUDDENLY NO ONE WANTED TO TOUCH.

18:44.794 --> 18:48.918
AND THEN HE TRACKED DOWN SOME
SUSPICIOUS OFFSHORE DEPOSITS

18:48.918 --> 18:50.840
MADE BY
ONE OF THEIR SENIOR V.P.s

18:50.840 --> 18:52.632
RIGHT AROUND
THE TIME OF THE SALE.

18:52.632 --> 18:54.344
SO NAVILET
BRIBED THE CONSUL

18:54.344 --> 18:56.756
TO TAKE THE OUTDATED VACCINE
OFF THEIR HANDS?

18:56.756 --> 18:58.258
THAT WAS SCOTT'S THEORY.

19:00.260 --> 19:03.263
DO YOU KNOW WHO AT NAVILET
NEGOTIATED THE VACCINE DEAL?

19:04.354 --> 19:07.267
I ASSURE YOU,
MY CLIENT DIDN'T BRIBE ANYONE.

19:07.267 --> 19:10.069
MR. SLOANE IS NAVILET'S
SENIOR VICE-PRESIDENT OF SALES.

19:10.069 --> 19:12.192
HE WOULDN'T RISK
HIS OR THE COMPANY'S REPUTATION

19:12.192 --> 19:15.445
ON A VACCINE DEAL WORTH --
WHAT, $50 MILLION?

19:15.445 --> 19:17.156
I TOLD THE CONSUL
SIX MONTHS AGO

19:17.156 --> 19:19.699
THAT I'D GIVE HIM A DISCOUNTED
PRICE ON BACTRA-VOX.

19:19.699 --> 19:21.621
BUT DEMAND WAS HIGH,

19:21.621 --> 19:24.374
AND IT WAS GONNA BE EIGHT WEEKS
BEFORE THE ORDER WAS FULFILLED.

19:24.374 --> 19:28.167
THE CONSUL TOLD ME THAT CHOLERA
SEASON WAS FAST APPROACHING

19:28.167 --> 19:30.290
AND HIS GOVERNMENT
JUST COULDN'T WAIT THAT LONG.

19:30.290 --> 19:32.592
SO HE AGREED
TO PURCHASE NUMORAL,

19:32.592 --> 19:35.345
HOPING IT WOULD BE
AS EFFECTIVE.

19:35.345 --> 19:38.348
UNFORTUNATELY, WE ALL KNOW HOW
THAT TURNED OUT. IT'S TRAGIC.

19:38.348 --> 19:40.720
OH, COME ON,
YOU HAD INSIDE INFORMATION

19:40.720 --> 19:44.013
THAT THE OLD VACCINE WAS ABOUT
TO BE YANKED BY THE W.H.O.,

19:44.013 --> 19:45.645
SO YOU PAID OFF THE CONSUL
TO TAKE IT.

19:45.645 --> 19:48.067
I ASSUME YOU WORK ON COMMISSION,
SO WHO CARES

19:48.067 --> 19:50.360
IF A FEW POOR PEOPLE DIE SO THAT
YOU CAN LINE YOUR POCKETS?

19:50.360 --> 19:51.981
DANIEL.

19:51.981 --> 19:53.983
I UNDERSTAND THE IMPULSE
TO FIND A BAD GUY, DR. PIERCE,

19:53.983 --> 19:57.317
BUT WHAT YOU'RE ALLEGING
SIMPLY ISN'T TRUE.

19:57.317 --> 20:00.119
WE DONATE MILLIONS OF DOLLARS
OF LIFESAVING MEDICINES

20:00.119 --> 20:01.781
EVERY YEAR.

20:01.781 --> 20:04.123
AND WE REINVEST A SIGNIFICANT
AMOUNT OF OUR PROFITS

20:04.123 --> 20:06.035
TO HELP IMPROVE
THE LIVING CONDITIONS

20:06.035 --> 20:07.827
OF PEOPLE
IN DEVELOPING COUNTRIES.

20:07.827 --> 20:10.039
OH, SPARE ME THE CORPORATE
BULLSHIT. YOU BRIBED THE CONSUL.

20:10.039 --> 20:12.171
WHEN THE REPORTER FOUND OUT
ABOUT IT, YOU HAD HIM KILLED.

20:12.171 --> 20:13.833
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?
WHAT?
WHAT I HAVEN'T
FIGURED OUT IS,

20:13.833 --> 20:15.505
WHY WOULD YOU
KILL THE CONSUL, TOO?

20:15.505 --> 20:17.096
I DIDN'T KILL ANYONE.

20:17.096 --> 20:20.099
OH, COME ON. WHAT ELSE --
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

20:25.184 --> 20:26.726
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

20:26.726 --> 20:28.518
THEY'RE LYING
THROUGH THEIR TEETH.

20:28.518 --> 20:30.440
AND YOU ARE MAKING
WILD ACCUSATIONS.

20:30.440 --> 20:32.982
SLOANE PAID OFF THE CONSUL --
WHY WOULD HE KILL HIM?

20:32.982 --> 20:34.734
MAYBE THE CONSUL
HAD A CHANGE OF HEART

20:34.734 --> 20:37.156
AND THREATENED TO COME CLEAN
AFTER ALL THOSE PEOPLE DIED.

20:37.156 --> 20:39.118
OR MAYBE HE JUST DEMANDED
A BIGGER KICKBACK.

20:39.118 --> 20:41.200
ASSUMING A KICKBACK HAPPENED
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

20:41.200 --> 20:42.702
UNTIL WE HAVE EVIDENCE,

20:42.702 --> 20:45.285
IT'S JUST SPECULATION
FROM A DEAD REPORTER.

20:45.285 --> 20:46.996
BUT...

20:46.996 --> 20:48.998
IF THE CONSUL
DID TAKE A KICKBACK

20:48.998 --> 20:51.250
AND HE SUDDENLY
CAME INTO A LOT OF MONEY,

20:51.250 --> 20:53.172
MAYBE HE STARTED
SPENDING IT.

20:53.172 --> 20:55.134
SOMEONE WOULD'VE NOTICED.

20:55.134 --> 20:58.678
LIKE THE WOMAN
WHO HANDLES ALL OF HIS AFFAIRS.

20:58.678 --> 21:02.091
THE CONSUL WAS NOT GREEDY.
HE LED A SIMPLE LIFE.

21:02.091 --> 21:05.935
SO YOU NEVER NOTICED ANY CHANGE
IN HIS FINANCIAL AFFAIRS --

21:05.935 --> 21:09.058
AN INVESTMENT IN REAL ESTATE
OR AN OFFSHORE ACCOUNT?

21:09.058 --> 21:10.600
NO.

21:10.600 --> 21:13.353
NONE OF US JOINED
THE FOREIGN SERVICE TO GET RICH.

21:13.353 --> 21:15.855
THE CONSUL BELIEVED
THAT HIS PURPOSE IN LIFE

21:15.855 --> 21:17.196
WAS HELPING OTHERS.

21:17.196 --> 21:18.858
PERHAPS
HE CHANGED HIS MIND?

21:18.858 --> 21:20.820
I DON'T THINK SO.

21:20.820 --> 21:22.862
WHY ARE YOU ASKING
THESE QUESTIONS?

21:22.862 --> 21:26.165
[ SIGHS ] WE THINK THE CONSUL
MAY HAVE ACCEPTED A BRIBE

21:26.165 --> 21:29.168
IN EXCHANGE FOR BUYING
OUTDATED CHOLERA VACCINES.

21:30.870 --> 21:32.622
NO.

21:32.622 --> 21:34.003
NO, I CANNOT BELIEVE

21:34.003 --> 21:36.876
THAT HE WOULD BETRAY OUR COUNTRY
FOR MONEY.

21:36.876 --> 21:40.840
MANY OF US LOST PEOPLE
THAT WE LOVE IN THE EPIDEMIC.

21:40.840 --> 21:45.595
OFFICER MEHTA --
HE LOST A SON AND A DAUGHTER.

21:45.595 --> 21:47.226
I LOST A COUSIN.

21:47.226 --> 21:50.269
AND HOW DID THE CONSUL REACT
TO ALL THIS?

21:51.931 --> 21:55.314
HE GRIEVED WITH US.

21:55.314 --> 21:57.397
IT DOES NOT MAKE SENSE.

21:57.397 --> 21:59.068
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

22:01.280 --> 22:04.073
RASHID.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

22:04.073 --> 22:07.617
IT'S MY JOB TO LOOK AFTER
THE WELFARE OF OUR CITIZENS.

22:07.617 --> 22:11.120
WHY ARE YOU TALKING TO THE FBI
WITHOUT YOUR ATTORNEY?

22:11.120 --> 22:12.502
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

22:12.502 --> 22:14.454
DR. PIERCE
AND AGENT MORETTI --

22:14.454 --> 22:16.045
THEY DON'T BELIEVE
I'M GUILTY.

22:16.045 --> 22:18.458
THEN WHY ARE YOU HERE?

22:18.458 --> 22:20.380
WE'RE INVESTIGATING
A DEAL

22:20.380 --> 22:23.342
THAT YOUR CONSUL MADE
WITH NAVILET PHARMACEUTICALS.

22:23.342 --> 22:24.844
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT IT?

22:24.844 --> 22:26.886
I'M AWARE THE CONSUL
AUTHORIZED THE PURCHASE

22:26.886 --> 22:29.058
OF A VACCINE FOR CHOLERA,
BUT THAT'S ALL I KNOW.

22:29.058 --> 22:30.229
[ RETCHES ]

22:31.811 --> 22:34.564
NASIM?
ARE YOU OKAY?

22:37.817 --> 22:39.399
WE SHOULD GO.

22:41.070 --> 22:43.322
NASIM?

22:43.322 --> 22:45.324
NASIM GETS SICK, AND YOU GO
RUNNING OUT OF THE ROOM?

22:45.324 --> 22:46.946
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT?

22:46.946 --> 22:50.079
NASIM THREW UP, BUT SHE'S NOT
THE ONLY ONE THAT FELT SICK.

22:53.663 --> 22:56.706
HOW DO YOU KNOW NASIM
DIDN'T JUST EAT SOME
BAD CHICKEN FOR LUNCH?

22:56.706 --> 22:58.498
SHE THREW UP
AT THE PRECISE MOMENT

22:58.498 --> 23:00.339
WE TOLD RASHID
ABOUT THE DRUG DEAL.

23:00.339 --> 23:02.341
SHE WAS MIRRORING HIS FEELINGS.
HE WAS ANXIOUS.

23:02.341 --> 23:03.883
YEAH, BECAUSE
HE WAS THE OFFICIAL

23:03.883 --> 23:05.635
TAKING KICKBACKS
FROM THE DRUG COMPANY.

23:05.635 --> 23:07.597
OKAY,
BUT AS I UNDERSTAND IT,

23:07.597 --> 23:09.969
THE CONSUL WOULD'VE
HAD TO SIGN OFF ON THIS DEAL,

23:09.969 --> 23:12.892
SO WHY WOULD THE NUMBER-TWO GUY
BE THE ONE GETTING KICKBACKS?

23:12.892 --> 23:15.475
MAYBE THEY WERE CO-CONSPIRATORS,
SPLITTING THE MONEY.

23:15.475 --> 23:16.896
WE DON'T KNOW YET.

23:16.896 --> 23:18.397
AT THE VERY LEAST,
RASHID KNEW ABOUT IT.

23:18.397 --> 23:20.359
THINK ABOUT IT --
SLOANE SELLS $50 MILLION

23:20.359 --> 23:22.652
WORTH OF USELESS VACCINES
AT -- WHAT, 2% COMMISSION?

23:22.652 --> 23:24.283
THAT'S A MILLION DOLLARS.

23:24.283 --> 23:26.405
THEN HE PAYS OFF THE VICE-CONSUL
TO PUSH THE DEAL THROUGH.

23:26.405 --> 23:28.988
WELL, IT'S A NICE THEORY.
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

23:28.988 --> 23:31.871
YOU CAN START WITH A SUBPOENA
FOR NAVILET'S FINANCIAL RECORDS,

23:31.871 --> 23:33.412
SEE IF THEY SHOW
THE DEPOSITS

23:33.412 --> 23:35.535
THAT SLOANE MADE
INTO THAT OFFSHORE ACCOUNT.

23:35.535 --> 23:37.246
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

23:37.246 --> 23:39.459
NO JUDGE IS GOING TO SIGN OFF
ON A FISHING EXPEDITION

23:39.459 --> 23:41.751
AGAINST ONE OF
THE BIGGEST COMPANIES IN TOWN.

23:41.751 --> 23:44.674
WELL, IF WE CAN'T GO AFTER
NAVILET, THEN LET'S GET
RASHID'S FINANCIALS.

23:44.674 --> 23:47.006
HE'S A DIPLOMAT
FOR A SOVEREIGN NATION.

23:47.006 --> 23:49.178
WE START DIGGING AROUND THERE
WITHOUT EVIDENCE,

23:49.178 --> 23:51.390
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
I'LL BE GETTING CALLS
FROM THE STATE DEPARTMENT.

23:51.390 --> 23:52.431
MORETTI.

23:52.431 --> 23:54.103
YEAH.

23:54.103 --> 23:56.435
LOOK, I WANT TO HELP YOU GUYS.
YOU KNOW THIS.

23:56.435 --> 23:59.018
BUT YOU GOT TO BRING ME MORE
THAN A PUDDLE OF PUKE.

23:59.018 --> 24:00.560
GOT IT. YES.

24:00.560 --> 24:02.401
I'M ON IT.

24:02.401 --> 24:04.233
I'M SORRY. WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO
TALK ABOUT THIS LATER.

24:04.233 --> 24:07.156
DANIEL, I'VE GOT ANOTHER CASE
I NEED YOUR HELP WITH.

24:12.121 --> 24:13.372
WE HAVE A NEW CASE?

24:13.372 --> 24:15.535
YES -- THE CASE
OF THE MISSING VOWS.

24:15.535 --> 24:16.746
WHAT?

24:16.746 --> 24:18.457
THAT WAS FATHER PAT
ON THE PHONE.

24:18.457 --> 24:20.339
I WAS SUPPOSED TO
HAVE MY WEDDING VOWS
TO HIM TWO DAYS AGO,

24:20.339 --> 24:23.002
AND I'VE WRITTEN THOUSANDS OF
VERSIONS, BUT ALL OF THEM SUCK.

24:23.002 --> 24:25.004
NOW, YOU ARE
A GREAT WRITER.

24:25.004 --> 24:26.846
YOU COME UP WITH
ALL OF THESE BRILLIANT LECTURES.

24:26.846 --> 24:28.257
OH, NO. NO, NO, NO.
I'M DESPERATE.

24:28.257 --> 24:30.389
I'M NOT WRITING
YOUR WEDDING VOWS FOR YOU.

24:30.389 --> 24:31.681
I DON'T SEE WHY NOT.

24:31.681 --> 24:33.052
BECAUSE IT'S WRONG
ON SO MANY LEVELS.

24:33.052 --> 24:34.684
I WOULDN'T EVEN --
MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING HERE

24:34.684 --> 24:36.355
THAT YOU COULD JUST USE
AS A JUMPING-OFF POINT.

24:36.355 --> 24:38.477
KATE, I --

24:38.477 --> 24:41.561
DANIEL, PLEASE. I HAVE ALREADY
LET DONNIE DOWN SO MANY TIMES.

24:41.561 --> 24:44.564
I AM BEGGING YOU HERE. YOU ARE
THE ONLY ONE WHO CAN HELP ME.

24:51.160 --> 24:53.162
[ TYPEWRITER CLACKING,
DINGING ]

24:57.166 --> 24:59.829
"TODAY, I PROMISE MYSELF
TO YOU AND THIS MARRIAGE.

24:59.829 --> 25:01.791
"TO BE FAITHFUL, LOVING,
AND TRUE,

25:01.791 --> 25:04.213
"WITHOUT ANY OF
THE INCREASED BRAIN ACTIVITY

25:04.213 --> 25:06.626
"THAT'S ASSOCIATED
WITH HESITATION OR DOUBT.

25:06.626 --> 25:08.628
"A TRUE PROMISE,
MADE IN EARNEST,

25:08.628 --> 25:10.630
"LITERALLY
PUTS THE BRAIN AT EASE.

25:10.630 --> 25:13.472
"AND IF YOU COULD SCAN
MY ANTERIOR CINGULATE CORTEX

25:13.472 --> 25:15.094
"RIGHT NOW, DONNIE, YOU'D SEE

25:15.094 --> 25:17.436
THAT IT HAS NEVER BEEN
MORE RELAXED."

25:17.436 --> 25:20.139
[ SCOFFS ]
MATE, THAT IS AWFUL.

25:20.139 --> 25:21.771
WHO ASKED YOU?

25:21.771 --> 25:24.313
NO, I'M JUST SAYING, YOU KNOW,
ARE YOU WRITING WEDDING VOWS

25:24.313 --> 25:25.945
OR THE WORLD'S
WORST GREETING CARD?

25:25.945 --> 25:27.276
YOU THINK
YOU COULD DO BETTER?

25:27.276 --> 25:29.028
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT.
I CAN'T.

25:30.109 --> 25:32.612
BUT RUMI CAN.

25:32.612 --> 25:35.995
"IN YOUR LIGHT,
I LEARN HOW TO LOVE.

25:35.995 --> 25:38.918
"IN YOUR BEAUTY,
HOW TO MAKE POEMS.

25:38.918 --> 25:43.713
YOU DANCE INSIDE MY CHEST,
WHERE NO ONE SEES YOU."

25:43.713 --> 25:45.965
I THINK
I'M GONNA THROW UP.

25:45.965 --> 25:47.546
YOU OKAY, DOC?

25:47.546 --> 25:49.719
I'M FINE.

25:49.719 --> 25:51.300
YOU SURE?

25:51.300 --> 25:53.552
'CAUSE IF YOU'RE NOT FEELING
WELL, I CAN JUST GET YOU --

25:53.552 --> 25:56.676
LEWICKI. LEWICKI, LEWICKI,
I'M FINE. JUST...GET LOST.

25:57.887 --> 25:59.889
ALL RIGHT.

25:59.889 --> 26:03.142
Australian:
YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULD REALLY
SHOW THAT GUY SOME RESPECT.

26:03.142 --> 26:05.274
YOU KNOW, IT'S ALWAYS
"LEWICKI THIS, LEWICKI THAT."

26:05.274 --> 26:07.647
WHY DON'T YOU TRY CALLING HIM
BY HIS FIRST NAME FOR ONCE?

26:07.647 --> 26:09.448
I HAVE CALLED HIM
BY HIS --

26:11.240 --> 26:13.402
HIS FIRST NAME.

26:14.573 --> 26:16.195
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

26:20.039 --> 26:23.002
HELLO, DR. PIERCE,
AGENT M--

26:25.254 --> 26:27.376
YOU'RE UPSET, DOCTOR.

26:27.376 --> 26:29.008
DID I DO SOMETHING WRONG?

26:29.008 --> 26:30.419
YOU DIDN'T TELL US
THE TRUTH

26:30.419 --> 26:33.012
ABOUT YOUR RELATIONSHIP
WITH VICE-CONSUL PRASAD.

26:34.513 --> 26:36.095
THERE'S NOTHING TO TELL.

26:36.095 --> 26:38.217
I'VE NOTICED HOW FORMAL YOU ARE
WHEN YOU TALK TO PEOPLE,

26:38.217 --> 26:40.099
ALWAYS ADDRESSING THEM
BY THEIR PROPER TITLES --

26:40.099 --> 26:43.022
"DR. PIERCE," "AGENT MORETTI,"
"MR. KHAN."

26:43.022 --> 26:47.396
BUT YOU CALL THE VICE-CONSUL
BY HIS FIRST NAME -- RASHID.

26:47.396 --> 26:49.108
AND NOW YOU'RE BLUSHING.

26:49.108 --> 26:52.111
I DON'T HAVE TO BE A SYNESTHETE
TO FIGURE OUT WHAT THAT MEANS.

26:52.111 --> 26:54.573
YOU'RE IN LOVE WITH HIM,
YES?

26:54.573 --> 26:57.196
MM. WE HAVE BEEN
SEEING EACH OTHER.

26:57.196 --> 26:59.699
BUT I AM HINDU,
AND HE IS MUSLIM,

26:59.699 --> 27:02.371
AND OUR FAMILIES NEVER WOULD
APPROVE, SO WE KEPT IT QUIET.

27:02.371 --> 27:04.243
YOU SENSED
HOW NERVOUS RASHID WAS

27:04.243 --> 27:06.295
WHEN WE BROUGHT UP
THE VACCINE DEAL.

27:06.295 --> 27:08.207
WE THINK
HE'S HIDING SOMETHING.

27:08.207 --> 27:09.378
HIDING WHAT?

27:09.378 --> 27:10.840
THAT HE WAS INVOLVED

27:10.840 --> 27:12.631
IN THE MURDERS OF THE CONSUL
AND THE REPORTER.

27:12.631 --> 27:14.553
[ SCOFFS ] WHAT?

27:14.553 --> 27:15.554
NO.

27:15.554 --> 27:17.847
RASHID IS NOT A KILLER.

27:17.847 --> 27:19.679
HE WAS NOT THE ONLY ONE
WHO WAS NERVOUS.

27:19.679 --> 27:21.220
I WAS NERVOUS, TOO, BE--

27:21.220 --> 27:23.973
BECAUSE OF WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE CONTRACT.

27:23.973 --> 27:26.225
THE CONTRACT
WITH NAVILET?

27:26.225 --> 27:28.818
WHAT HAPPENED TO IT?

27:28.818 --> 27:31.731
RASHID CAME TO THE OFFICE
TO PICK IT UP.

27:31.731 --> 27:36.075
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO DELIVER IT
TO THE DRUG COMPANY.

27:36.075 --> 27:39.578
HE BROUGHT ME A COFFEE,
AS HE SOMETIMES DOES.

27:44.744 --> 27:46.415
I WAS TERRIFIED.

27:46.415 --> 27:48.087
I KNEW THAT THE CONSUL
WOULD LOSE HIS TEMPER

27:48.087 --> 27:50.419
IF HE FOUND OUT
THE PAPERWORK WAS RUINED.

27:50.419 --> 27:52.341
OH, WHAT AM I GOING TO DO?

27:52.341 --> 27:54.673
HE'LL FIRE ME. HE'LL SEND ME
BACK TO BANGLADESH.

27:54.673 --> 27:56.345
I WON'T LET THAT HAPPEN.

27:56.345 --> 27:58.758
IT'S OKAY.
I'VE GOT ANOTHER COPY.

27:58.758 --> 28:00.679
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

28:00.679 --> 28:02.221
THE CONSUL GAVE ME A COPY
TO REVIEW.

28:02.221 --> 28:03.682
IT'S IN MY OFFICE.
I'LL GET IT.

28:03.682 --> 28:06.435
ALL YOU NEED TO DO
IS SIGN FOR HIM.

28:07.646 --> 28:10.109
YOU'VE SIGNED HIS NAME BEFORE,
HAVEN'T YOU?

28:19.949 --> 28:22.872
THE CONSUL TOLD THE REPORTER
THE TRUTH AFTER ALL.

28:22.872 --> 28:24.453
HE DID BUY
THE NEW VACCINE.

28:24.453 --> 28:26.085
OR AT LEAST
HE THOUGHT HE WAS BUYING IT

28:26.085 --> 28:27.416
WHEN HE SIGNED
THE PAPERWORK.

28:27.416 --> 28:29.378
I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

28:29.378 --> 28:31.090
THE CONTRACT
THAT RASHID BROUGHT YOU,

28:31.090 --> 28:33.212
THE ONE YOU FORGED
THE CONSUL'S SIGNATURE ON,

28:33.212 --> 28:34.964
WAS FOR THE OLD VACCINE.

28:38.677 --> 28:40.339
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

28:42.431 --> 28:44.603
ALL THOSE PEOPLE
WHO DIED...

28:46.896 --> 28:48.687
...I AM TO BLAME.

28:48.687 --> 28:51.350
YOU COULDN'T HAVE KNOWN.
RASHID WAS USING YOU.

28:51.350 --> 28:53.562
BUT IF HIS FEELINGS
WERE NOT REAL,

28:53.562 --> 28:56.946
I SHOULD'VE BEEN ABLE TO TELL --
BECAUSE OF MY CONDITION.

28:56.946 --> 28:58.657
HIS FEELINGS FOR YOU
MIGHT BE REAL.

28:58.657 --> 29:00.359
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
HE'S NOT A KILLER.

29:05.624 --> 29:08.707
THIS DOESN'T PROVE ANYTHING.
WE'LL SUBPOENA THE CONTRACT.

29:08.707 --> 29:10.369
HANDWRITING ANALYSIS WILL PROVE
THAT NASIM SIGNED IT.

29:10.369 --> 29:11.871
YOU SWITCHED OUT
THOSE CONTRACTS, MR. PRASAD.

29:11.871 --> 29:13.833
NASIM ALSO TOLD US

29:13.833 --> 29:16.375
THAT YOU BROKERED THE DEAL
WITH NAVILET,

29:16.375 --> 29:19.638
THAT YOU MET WITH GORDON SLOANE
A HALF A DOZEN TIMES.

29:19.638 --> 29:22.051
YOU COOKED UP THIS SCAM
TOGETHER, DIDN'T YOU?

29:22.051 --> 29:23.843
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.
IT WAS A WIN-WIN.

29:23.843 --> 29:26.645
SLOANE SELLS A WAREHOUSE
FULL OF DRUGS THAT NOBODY WANTS,

29:26.645 --> 29:28.057
AND YOU GET A BIG KICKBACK.

29:28.057 --> 29:29.768
IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE WE FIND

29:29.768 --> 29:32.731
THAT OFFSHORE ACCOUNT
AND LINK IT BACK TO YOU.

29:32.731 --> 29:35.274
I SAW THAT SILVER MERCEDES
PARKED IN YOUR SPOT.

29:35.274 --> 29:37.156
THAT DOES SEEM
A LITTLE BIT OBVIOUS, THOUGH,

29:37.156 --> 29:38.157
DON'T YOU THINK?

29:39.568 --> 29:41.110
AFTER THE REPORTER

29:41.110 --> 29:43.032
THREATENED TO BLOW THE LID
OFF YOUR LITTLE SCHEME,

29:43.032 --> 29:45.074
YOU REALIZED THAT YOU HAD TO
KILL HIM AND THE CONSUL.

29:45.074 --> 29:46.665
I DIDN'T KILL ANYONE.

29:46.665 --> 29:49.168
IF YOU'VE GOT EVIDENCE,
THEN YOU CHARGE ME. OTHERWISE --

29:49.168 --> 29:50.749
NO ONE SAID ANYTHING
ABOUT CHARGING YOU.

29:50.749 --> 29:52.962
THE STATE DEPARTMENT
WILL HAVE YOU EXPELLED.

29:52.962 --> 29:54.753
I'M SURE
THE BANGLADESHI GOVERNMENT

29:54.753 --> 29:56.545
WILL BE THRILLED
TO HAVE YOU BACK

29:56.545 --> 29:59.798
WHEN THEY LEARN ABOUT YOUR PLAN
AND ALL THE LIVES IT COST.

29:59.798 --> 30:01.800
OH, AND DON'T THINK
GORDON SLOANE IS GONNA HELP YOU.

30:01.800 --> 30:04.013
HE'S GOT MILLIONS OF DOLLARS
TO SPEND ON LAWYERS,

30:04.013 --> 30:06.725
AND THEY ARE ALL TELLING HIM TO
LET YOU TAKE THE FALL FOR THIS.

30:10.980 --> 30:13.312
[ SIGHS ]

30:13.312 --> 30:15.144
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

30:15.144 --> 30:16.525
TESTIFY AGAINST SLOANE.

30:16.525 --> 30:18.317
THE U.S. ATTORNEY
HAS ASSURED ME

30:18.317 --> 30:19.939
THAT IF YOU COOPERATE,

30:19.939 --> 30:22.491
YOU'LL SERVE A REDUCED SENTENCE
IN A U.S. PRISON.

30:22.491 --> 30:24.533
[ SIGHS ]

30:26.535 --> 30:29.038
LOOK...

30:29.038 --> 30:31.040
I DIDN'T KNOW
THIS NEW STRAIN OF CHOLERA

30:31.040 --> 30:33.542
WAS GOING TO SPREAD
TO MY COUNTRY --

30:33.542 --> 30:35.414
CERTAINLY NOT THIS FAST.

30:35.414 --> 30:38.507
EVENTUALLY, THE NEW STRAIN
MAY FIND ITS WAY TO SOUTH ASIA,

30:38.507 --> 30:40.759
BUT IN MY OPINION,
IT'S NOT SOMETHING

30:40.759 --> 30:43.342
YOUR GOVERNMENT
SHOULD WORRY ABOUT RIGHT NOW.

30:43.342 --> 30:46.425
THE NUMORAL VACCINE WILL
MEET YOUR NEEDS. I ASSURE YOU.

30:46.425 --> 30:47.887
BUT BACTRA-VOX
IS EFFECTIVE

30:47.887 --> 30:49.848
AGAINST THE NEWER
CHOLERA STRAINS.

30:49.848 --> 30:51.931
HOW CAN I JUSTIFY
BUYING ONE THAT ISN'T,

30:51.931 --> 30:53.772
ESPECIALLY
IF THE PRICE IS THE SAME?

30:53.772 --> 30:55.684
DON'T YOU WANT TO SELL ME
YOUR BEST PRODUCT?

30:55.684 --> 30:58.067
WELL, THE TRUTH IS,

30:58.067 --> 31:00.940
WE'VE HAD SOME PROBLEMS
PRODUCING THE NEW VACCINE.

31:00.940 --> 31:02.531
THERE'S A BACKLOG.

31:02.531 --> 31:04.403
IT'LL BE MONTHS
BEFORE IT'S AVAILABLE

31:04.403 --> 31:06.445
IN THE QUANTITIES
THAT YOU NEED.

31:06.445 --> 31:08.287
THEN I GUESS
I'LL HAVE TO SEE

31:08.287 --> 31:10.449
WHAT YOUR COMPETITORS
ARE OFFERING.

31:10.449 --> 31:13.122
HOLD ON.

31:13.122 --> 31:16.625
IF YOU WERE WILLING
TO CONSIDER THE OLDER DRUG,

31:16.625 --> 31:21.590
I MIGHT BE ABLE
TO OFFER YOU...AN INCENTIVE.

31:25.764 --> 31:26.635
HOW MUCH?

31:29.268 --> 31:34.013
$100,000 TO MAKE SURE
THE CONTRACT WENT THROUGH.

31:34.013 --> 31:36.725
BUT I KNEW THE CONSUL
WOULDN'T SIGN THE CONTRACT.

31:36.725 --> 31:38.897
HE HAD ALL OF MY RESEARCH
ON THE VACCINES.

31:38.897 --> 31:40.519
SO YOU AND SLOANE
MADE THE CONSUL THINK

31:40.519 --> 31:42.191
HE WAS BUYING
THE NEW VACCINE.

31:42.191 --> 31:44.193
THEN YOU SWITCHED OUT THE
PAPERWORK TO COVER YOUR ASSES,

31:44.193 --> 31:46.735
SO IT LOOKED LIKE HE KNOWINGLY
BOUGHT THE OLDER DRUG.

31:46.735 --> 31:48.657
YOU AND NASIM WERE ALREADY
IN A RELATIONSHIP.

31:48.657 --> 31:50.239
SHE WAS IN LOVE WITH YOU.

31:50.239 --> 31:51.740
YOU KNEW THAT SHE'D FORGE
THE CONSUL'S SIGNATURE

31:51.740 --> 31:52.741
WHEN YOU ASKED.

31:52.741 --> 31:54.033
THEN THE DEAL WAS DONE.

31:54.033 --> 31:55.374
YOU THOUGHT
YOU WERE IN THE CLEAR,

31:55.374 --> 31:56.915
UNTIL THE REPORTER
SHOWED UP.

31:59.538 --> 32:01.500
YES.

32:01.500 --> 32:05.714
WHEN I OVERHEARD HIM
TALKING TO OUR SECURITY CHIEF,

32:05.714 --> 32:07.756
I KNEW WE HAD A PROBLEM.

32:07.756 --> 32:09.598
Mehta: I'M SORRY.

32:09.598 --> 32:12.471
Scott: YOU'RE NOT GONNA LET ME
TALK TO THE CONSUL? FINE.

32:12.471 --> 32:14.974
BUT YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOUR BOSS HAS DONE.

32:14.974 --> 32:17.646
HE TOOK A PAYOFF
TO SHIP A WORTHLESS VACCINE,

32:17.646 --> 32:19.728
AND NOW THOUSANDS
OF YOUR PEOPLE ARE DEAD.

32:19.728 --> 32:21.610
HE WAS ONTO THE SCHEME.

32:21.610 --> 32:24.733
SO I CALLED GORDON SLOANE.

32:24.733 --> 32:26.986
HE TOLD ME NOT TO WORRY,

32:26.986 --> 32:29.828
THAT HE HAD A GUY
WHO COULD TAKE CARE OF IT.

32:29.828 --> 32:32.161
BUT I THOUGHT THAT MEANT HE WAS
GOING TO BRIBE THE REPORTER.

32:32.161 --> 32:35.494
I NEVER THOUGHT FOR A SECOND
HE WAS GOING TO KILL HIM.

32:39.748 --> 32:42.001
Brooks:
LET ME GET THIS STRAIGHT.

32:42.001 --> 32:43.962
YOU THINK THAT YOU CAN CHARGE
MY CLIENT WITH TWO MURDERS

32:43.962 --> 32:45.844
BECAUSE OF
A COFFEE-STAINED CONTRACT

32:45.844 --> 32:47.676
THAT WAS REPLACED
WITH A CLEAN COPY?

32:47.676 --> 32:49.048
IT WASN'T A CLEAN COPY.

32:49.048 --> 32:51.220
IT WAS A COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT CONTRACT --

32:51.220 --> 32:52.891
ONE THE CONSUL
NEVER WOULD'VE SIGNED.

32:52.891 --> 32:54.973
REALLY?
THE CONSUL TELL YOU THAT?

32:54.973 --> 32:56.685
NO, YOUR CLIENT MADE SURE
THAT WOULDN'T BE POSSIBLE

32:56.685 --> 32:58.437
WHEN HE HAD
THE CONSUL KILLED.

32:58.437 --> 32:59.768
THIS IS ABSURD.

32:59.768 --> 33:01.100
MR. SLOANE WAS
AT A SHAREHOLDERS MEETING

33:01.100 --> 33:02.651
WHEN THE CONSUL WAS KILLED.

33:02.651 --> 33:04.563
THERE WAS AT LEAST 50 PEOPLE
WHO SAW HIM THERE.

33:04.563 --> 33:05.694
IT'S A MEANINGLESS ALIBI.

33:05.694 --> 33:07.106
YOU TOLD RASHID

33:07.106 --> 33:09.108
THAT YOU HAD A GUY
WHO COULD TAKE CARE OF IT.

33:09.108 --> 33:10.699
YOU HIRED A PROFESSIONAL.

33:10.699 --> 33:12.281
WE DON'T HAVE TO
LISTEN TO THIS.

33:12.281 --> 33:13.662
WE'RE GONNA PUT YOU IN JAIL
FOR FRAUD, SLOANE --

33:13.662 --> 33:15.574
5, MAYBE 7 YEARS.
TAKE YOUR BEST SHOT.

33:15.574 --> 33:18.117
AND AFTER YOU GET OUT,
WE'RE GONNA TURN YOU OVER
TO THE BANGLADESHIS.

33:19.538 --> 33:21.460
YEAH.

33:21.460 --> 33:23.882
THEY WANT YOU EXTRADITED TO FACE
FRAUD CHARGES IN THEIR COUNTRY.

33:23.882 --> 33:25.834
NO REASON FOR US
TO STAND IN THEIR WAY.

33:25.834 --> 33:29.548
THING IS ABOUT
THE BANGLADESHI COURT SYSTEM --

33:29.548 --> 33:31.220
IT'S EXTREMELY UNDERSTAFFED.

33:31.220 --> 33:34.223
IT COULD TAKE YEARS
FOR YOUR CASE TO COME TO TRIAL.

33:34.223 --> 33:37.726
AND ALL THAT TIME, YOU'LL BE
SITTING IN A BANGLADESHI PRISON.

33:41.140 --> 33:44.233
MUST BE ALL KINDS OF DISEASES
YOU COULD CATCH IN THERE.

33:44.233 --> 33:47.066
BETTER MAKE SURE YOUR
VACCINATIONS ARE UP TO DATE.

33:49.148 --> 33:50.739
CAN THEY DO THAT?

33:51.820 --> 33:53.242
WHAT ARE YOU OFFERING?

33:58.287 --> 34:00.789
YOUR CLIENT GIVES US THE NAME
OF THE KILLER HE HIRED

34:00.789 --> 34:03.162
AND PLEADS GUILTY
TO SOLICITATION FOR MURDER.

34:08.167 --> 34:10.259
WHY DON'T YOU GUYS
TAKE A FEW MINUTES?

34:12.341 --> 34:15.804
[ DOOR OPENS ]

34:18.977 --> 34:20.309
THINK HE'LL FOLD?

34:20.309 --> 34:22.101
I THINK WE GOT
A PRETTY DECENT SHOT.

34:22.101 --> 34:23.772
IT -- IT STILL DOESN'T
ADD UP.

34:23.772 --> 34:25.604
WHAT?

34:25.604 --> 34:28.107
RASHID TOLD US THAT
THE CONSUL HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THE SCHEME.

34:28.107 --> 34:30.779
SO...
WHY DID SLOANE KILL HIM?

34:30.779 --> 34:33.492
WELL,
MAYBE THE CONSUL CAUGHT ON

34:33.492 --> 34:35.954
AFTER THE REPORTER CAME
TO SEE HIM THE FIRST TIME.

34:35.954 --> 34:39.198
Australian:
YOU KNOW, THE CAPITALIST
ECONOMY IS DISGUSTING.

34:39.198 --> 34:40.199
WHAT?

34:40.199 --> 34:42.000
DANIEL, ARE YOU OKAY?

34:42.000 --> 34:46.004
YOUR COUNTRY GIVES CORPORATIONS
THE SAME RIGHTS AS PEOPLE.

34:46.004 --> 34:48.337
BUT PEOPLE ARE FLESH AND BLOOD,
MATE, YOU KNOW?

34:48.337 --> 34:50.339
THEY'RE -- THEY'RE --
THEY'RE -- THEY'RE MOTHERS,

34:50.339 --> 34:53.212
AND THEY'RE FATHERS
AND THEY'RE CHILDREN.

34:55.714 --> 34:57.886
OUR DRUG SALESMAN
HAS BLOOD ON HIS HANDS.

35:00.018 --> 35:01.980
BUT IT'S NOT THE CONSUL'S.

35:04.433 --> 35:06.565
THE U.S. ATTORNEY
IS MOVING FORWARD

35:06.565 --> 35:08.987
WITH NASIM'S PROSECUTION.

35:08.987 --> 35:13.692
BUT DR. PIERCE AND I
DON'T THINK THAT SHE DID IT.

35:13.692 --> 35:16.735
WE'RE WONDERING IF THERE'S
ANYTHING ELSE THAT YOU REMEMBER,

35:16.735 --> 35:18.577
IF YOU CAN THINK
OF ANYONE ELSE

35:18.577 --> 35:21.330
WHO MIGHT'VE WANTED
TO HURT THE CONSUL.

35:21.330 --> 35:23.332
OH. UM...

35:25.334 --> 35:27.246
I'M SORRY.
I-I CAN'T THINK OF ANYONE.

35:27.246 --> 35:30.629
MR. MEHTA, WE UNDERSTAND THAT
YOU LOST A SON AND A DAUGHTER

35:30.629 --> 35:32.511
IN THE CHOLERA EPIDEMIC.

35:35.053 --> 35:36.385
HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT?

35:36.385 --> 35:37.806
NASIM.

35:37.806 --> 35:39.258
WE'RE VERY SORRY.

35:41.760 --> 35:45.023
MY CHILDREN
HAD BEEN VACCINATED.

35:45.023 --> 35:46.895
THEY WERE
SUPPOSED TO BE SAFE.

35:46.895 --> 35:49.648
THE REPORTER TOLD YOU
THAT THE VACCINE

35:49.648 --> 35:52.691
THE CONSUL SUPPLIED
WAS OUT OF DATE, DIDN'T HE?

35:52.691 --> 35:55.274
I CAN ONLY IMAGINE
HOW YOU FELT.

35:55.274 --> 35:57.576
AND THEN WHEN YOU FOUND OUT
THAT THE MAN YOU WORKED FOR

35:57.576 --> 36:00.949
WAS RESPONSIBLE...
YOU MUST'VE BEEN OUTRAGED.

36:00.949 --> 36:03.412
THAT'S WHY YOU TOLD US
ABOUT THE REPORTER --

36:03.412 --> 36:05.704
SO THAT WE'D UNCOVER
THIS AWFUL CRIME.

36:05.704 --> 36:07.916
BUT YOU DIDN'T MENTION
YOUR CHILDREN

36:07.916 --> 36:11.340
BECAUSE YOU KNEW
THAT WOULD MAKE YOU A SUSPECT.

36:11.340 --> 36:13.882
YOU SEEM LIKE AN HONORABLE MAN,
NOT THE KIND

36:13.882 --> 36:17.095
THAT WOULD LET AN INNOCENT WOMAN
GO TO PRISON FOR MURDER.

36:17.095 --> 36:20.008
NASIM IS A DAUGHTER, TOO.

36:20.008 --> 36:22.601
HOW DO YOU THINK HER PARENTS
ARE GONNA FEEL IF THEY LOSE HER?

36:29.067 --> 36:32.311
IF I TELL YOU
WHAT HAPPENED...

36:32.311 --> 36:34.192
WILL THEY LET NASIM GO?

36:34.192 --> 36:36.525
DEPENDS WHAT YOU TELL US.

36:44.873 --> 36:50.709
AFTER THE REPORTER TOLD ME
ABOUT THIS...SCHEME...

36:50.709 --> 36:52.331
I WENT TO RASHID.

36:52.331 --> 36:53.832
I'M SHOCKED.

36:53.832 --> 36:55.924
I DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THESE KICKBACKS.

36:55.924 --> 36:57.546
HOW COULD YOU
LET THIS HAPPEN?!

36:57.546 --> 36:59.428
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED?!

36:59.428 --> 37:02.471
I TOLD THE CONSUL OUR PEOPLE
DESERVE THE NEWEST VACCINES,

37:02.471 --> 37:05.053
BUT HE WOULDN'T LISTEN
TO ME.

37:05.053 --> 37:06.605
NOW I KNOW WHY.

37:06.605 --> 37:08.226
HE CAN'T GET AWAY
WITH THIS.

37:08.226 --> 37:10.559
THE CONSUL'S FAMILY
IS POWERFUL.

37:10.559 --> 37:13.902
IF I GO TO OUR SUPERIORS,
NOTHING WILL COME OF IT,

37:13.902 --> 37:15.984
AND WE'LL BE SENT HOME.

37:15.984 --> 37:17.616
I THINK IT'S BEST

37:17.616 --> 37:19.318
IF WE JUST FORGET
THIS CONVERSATION HAPPENED.

37:19.318 --> 37:22.821
THAT'S WHEN I REALIZED
WHAT I HAD TO DO.

37:27.366 --> 37:29.368
FOR THE CONSUL,
DEATH WAS QUICK.

37:29.368 --> 37:31.039
FOR MY CHILDREN,
IT WAS NOT.

37:31.039 --> 37:33.672
I DIDN'T REALIZE
NASIM HAD COME RUNNING AFTER HIM

37:33.672 --> 37:35.003
AND HAD SEEN EVERYTHING.

37:39.588 --> 37:42.471
I DELIVERED JUSTICE.

37:42.471 --> 37:44.683
I CAN ACCEPT
THE CONSEQUENCES.

37:44.683 --> 37:46.725
RASHID LIED TO YOU.

37:46.725 --> 37:49.308
HE WAS THE ONE
WHO TOOK THE PAYOFF.

37:49.308 --> 37:53.191
THE CONSUL --
HE HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

37:58.276 --> 38:00.859
ARE YOU SAYING
I KILLED AN INNOCENT MAN?

38:19.047 --> 38:20.759
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

38:20.759 --> 38:23.972
THEY'RE TOUCHING
WITHOUT BEING SAPPY.

38:23.972 --> 38:26.304
THEY'RE JUST THE RIGHT AMOUNT
OF FUNNY.

38:26.304 --> 38:27.846
THEY ARE PERFECT!

38:27.846 --> 38:29.808
OF COURSE THEY ARE.
THEY'RE YOUR WORDS.

38:29.808 --> 38:33.021
I FOUND THIS
AT THE BACK OF YOUR JOURNAL.

38:33.021 --> 38:34.893
I DIDN'T CHANGE A THING.

38:36.985 --> 38:40.899
THIS IS ONE OF THE FIRST THINGS
THAT I WROTE.

38:40.899 --> 38:42.781
[ LAUGHS ]

38:42.781 --> 38:45.534
I WAS AT A PANCAKE HOUSE
ON MILWAUKEE,

38:45.534 --> 38:47.746
AND I WAS WAITING
FOR DONNIE TO SHOW UP,

38:47.746 --> 38:51.249
AND THE WORDS JUST...
CAME TO ME.

38:51.249 --> 38:52.330
THANK YOU.

38:54.833 --> 38:57.916
THERE'S NO WAY I COULD'VE
FIGURED THIS OUT WITHOUT YOU.

38:57.916 --> 38:59.798
OH,
DONNIE'S GONNA LOVE IT.

38:59.798 --> 39:02.511
[ DOOR OPENS ]
[ LAUGHS ]

39:02.511 --> 39:04.342
DOC?

39:04.342 --> 39:06.174
YOU HAVE A VISITOR.

39:07.846 --> 39:09.518
I'M GLAD
YOU'RE BOTH HERE.

39:09.518 --> 39:10.929
I WANTED TO THANK YOU

39:10.929 --> 39:13.351
FOR EVERYTHING
THAT YOU HAVE DONE FOR ME.

39:13.351 --> 39:14.773
OF COURSE.

39:14.773 --> 39:17.526
UH...IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME
ONE SECOND...

39:17.526 --> 39:19.357
MAX, IS THERE A FAX MACHINE
AROUND HERE?

39:19.357 --> 39:20.859
Max: SURE.

39:20.859 --> 39:22.360
GOT TO GET THESE
TO FATHER PAT.

39:27.486 --> 39:30.288
AGENT MORETTI IS
A SPECIAL WOMAN, ISN'T SHE?

39:30.288 --> 39:31.950
HMM.

39:34.082 --> 39:38.587
DR. PIERCE, IT IS NOT
MY PLACE TO SAY, BUT...

39:38.587 --> 39:40.959
PERHAPS YOU SHOULD TELL HER
HOW YOU REALLY FEEL.

39:42.380 --> 39:43.462
W--

39:47.265 --> 39:49.267
[ SCOFFS ] I --

39:49.267 --> 39:52.350
Daniel: THE POETS TELL US
TO LISTEN TO OUR HEART.

39:52.350 --> 39:53.391
WHAT A LOAD OF CRAP.

39:53.391 --> 39:55.063
[ LAUGHTER ]
SERIOUSLY.

39:55.063 --> 39:57.395
HAVE YOU EVER LISTENED TO ONE
THROUGH A STETHOSCOPE?

39:57.395 --> 39:59.107
IT'S JUST VALVES
OPENING AND CLOSING

39:59.107 --> 40:00.228
AND OPENING AND CLOSING.

40:00.228 --> 40:01.900
IT SOUNDS LIKE A SUMP PUMP.

40:01.900 --> 40:04.693
IT MAY FEEL LIKE
OUR EMOTIONS ARE DOWN HERE,

40:04.693 --> 40:06.404
BUT THEY'RE REALLY UP HERE,

40:06.404 --> 40:08.867
KNOCKING AROUND
OUR LIMBIC SYSTEMS.

40:08.867 --> 40:12.330
WHEN WE FACE THE HARD DECISIONS,
WE OFTEN HAVE TO CHOOSE

40:12.330 --> 40:16.665
BETWEEN THE EMOTIONAL RESPONSE
AND THE RATIONAL ONE.

40:16.665 --> 40:21.039
AND MORE OFTEN THAN NOT,
IT SEEMS EMOTION WINS THE DAY.

40:21.039 --> 40:24.092
SOME OF US ACT OUT OF GREED.

40:27.255 --> 40:31.850
OTHERS ARE MOTIVATED
BY RAGE OR REVENGE.

40:35.013 --> 40:37.936
SO, IF OUR FEELINGS
ARE THAT DESTRUCTIVE,

40:37.936 --> 40:40.438
MAYBE IT'S BETTER
IF WE HIDE THEM --

40:40.438 --> 40:45.113
TAMP THEM DOWN,
KEEP THEM FROM BOILING OVER.

40:45.113 --> 40:46.485
MAYBE.

40:47.826 --> 40:52.240
BUT CAN WE REALLY
DENY OUR EMOTIONS FOREVER?

41:19.558 --> 41:21.650
SOONER OR LATER,

41:21.650 --> 41:24.482
WILL THEY BUBBLE
TO THE SURFACE...

41:24.482 --> 41:26.695
AND FORCE US TO ACT?
